[title]: # (Hooks Guidelines)

Place all custom hooks in `hooks/`.

File naming: `useX.ts` (e.g., `useFilteredEvents.ts`)

Each hook should do one thing only.
Always prefix with `use`.
Examples:
- useFilteredEvents
- useDebouncedInput
- useFetchWithGPT
